{
  "stem": "1387.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was against my good judgment to go to the woods near Zloczow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had an, an incident.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the first day that we [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] came to the woods-- I came also with my girlfriend, Chana-- we found a Pole, a Christian, in the woods.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a debate between us whether we should get rid of him or let him live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, we were not aggressive enough, or some of us were not aggressive enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, he notified a police that we are in the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And within a few hours that same night, they surrounded the woods area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My girlfriend, Chana, was killed there, and most of them, most of the others were killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They threw in hand grenades and all kinds of-- they didn't dare walk into the woods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My teacher and I were able to escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm trying to go back to the time between the liquidation of the ghetto in Zloczow and the transfer of the [NON-ENGLISH] camp in Zloczow to Janowska.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, my teacher and I, of course, went back to Pobocz, to the area of the woods that I worked carrying water to the German Wehrmacht radio station.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew the woods there quite well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I acquired a spade-- a shovel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we made ourselves a very nice bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got some food with us, and we got-- we dug a, a bunker in the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A few days after this, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a young lady by the name of Frydka Brenner was caught.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Hauptsturmfuhrer Warzog was notified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came to look for us in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
